Mom, I got to go. I love you.

30:55.227 --> 30:56.660
Are you meditating?

30:59.231 --> 31:00.564
Are you kidding me?

31:00.599 --> 31:02.533
Geez. Grab his legs.

31:02.568 --> 31:04.234
Get th... Grab his feet.

31:04.270 --> 31:05.669
Deep breath.

31:08.207 --> 31:10.707
There's a delivery. Can you...
In the back.

31:12.845 --> 31:14.878
It's slippery. Goddamn ponytail.

31:14.914 --> 31:18.215
Sign for me right here.

31:19.618 --> 31:21.785
And the code.
Right, right. Sorry, sorry.

31:21.821 --> 31:24.154
Bryce, can you get back here?
I need your help over here.

31:30.896 --> 31:33.130
Grab his feet. It's gonna be all right.

31:36.402 --> 31:39.336
Are you sure you're okay?

31:39.371 --> 31:41.105
Yeah, I'm fine.

31:41.140 --> 31:43.373
You should probably
get yourself to an E.R.

31:43.409 --> 31:45.776
I will. A little later today.

31:47.513 --> 31:48.579
You saved that guy.

31:48.614 --> 31:50.747
You know, all in a day's work.

31:52.351 --> 31:53.550
Wow.

31:53.586 --> 31:55.814
Who left the stockroom door open?

31:56.255 --> 31:58.122
I let the delivery guy in.

31:58.157 --> 31:59.389
What?

32:24.926 --> 32:27.826
I mean, he was the first
black country star I ever met,

32:27.862 --> 32:31.030
and one ride on that mechanical bull,

32:33.633 --> 32:36.401
he swept me off my feet.

32:36.436 --> 32:38.169
It's just a shame he loved armed robbery

32:38.204 --> 32:40.004
as much as he did music.

32:40.040 --> 32:43.141
You know, he was the one
that introduced me to Jamal.

32:43.176 --> 32:45.276
I forgot about Jamal!

32:45.312 --> 32:49.280
Who's Jamal? He sounds delicious.

32:49.316 --> 32:51.683
Delicious and nutritious, okay?

32:52.886 --> 32:56.454
He was the first guy to ever propose.

32:56.489 --> 32:58.156
What happened?

32:58.191 --> 32:59.624
Well, his wife said

32:59.659 --> 33:02.026
our wedding wasn't a good idea, okay?

33:03.296 --> 33:04.596
Don't act like I'm the only one

33:04.631 --> 33:06.164
who ever dated a married man.

33:06.199 --> 33:07.966
- Come on, now.
- Present.

33:08.001 --> 33:09.400
Amen.

33:09.436 --> 33:12.270
My God. I was married for six years.

33:12.305 --> 33:14.739
What? You... You never told us that.

33:14.774 --> 33:15.873
What was she like?

33:15.909 --> 33:17.241
He.

33:17.277 --> 33:18.476
- Ann...
- What?

33:18.511 --> 33:20.612
He was a linguistics professor at Yale.

33:20.647 --> 33:24.148
And then when he started
screwing his T.A.,

33:24.184 --> 33:26.050
who I also happened to be screwing...

33:26.086 --> 33:27.518
There it is.

33:27.554 --> 33:29.687
Things went sideways.

33:30.657 --> 33:32.657
You guys have, like, lived.

33:32.692 --> 33:36.160
Shoot! You guys, we just lost
our reservation at Luques.

33:36.196 --> 33:37.428
- Shoot!
- Shoot.

33:37.464 --> 33:39.263
No one cares about the fancy dinner.

33:39.299 --> 33:41.532
I want to party with you girls, okay?

33:41.568 --> 33:43.501
Where do you guys go to get wild?

33:43.536 --> 33:46.771
I know just the place.

33:46.806 --> 33:50.241
But that tiara might be tipped
by the time we get through.

33:50.276 --> 33:51.309
Okay?

33:53.413 --> 33:54.879
Um, Desna, I've been wanting

33:54.914 --> 33:57.315
to ask you this question all night.

33:57.350 --> 33:58.616
Can I touch your hair?

33:58.652 --> 34:00.118
No.

34:09.362 --> 34:12.521
Whoo! Bachelorettes coming through!

34:12.576 --> 34:13.944
Shoo, shoo, shoo!

34:13.969 --> 34:14.969
Yeah!

34:15.001 --> 34:16.467
I'm talking about ladies!

34:55.014 --> 34:58.215
I have never seen Audrey so fired up.

34:58.251 --> 35:02.119
I mean, she does get wild
in Soul Cycle, but...

35:02.155 --> 35:03.654
She just made $5.

35:06.893 --> 35:09.894
Okay, that right there, though?

35:09.929 --> 35:11.495
That surprises me.

35:11.531 --> 35:13.164
Not me.

35:13.199 --> 35:16.667
Quiet Ann looks exactly
like her husband.

35:18.571 --> 35:20.704
Okay.

35:20.740 --> 35:22.406
Thank you for this.

35:22.442 --> 35:23.774
You're welcome.

35:23.810 --> 35:26.310
And, you know, Luques would have boring,

35:26.345 --> 35:28.646
and then half those women
would have thrown it up

35:28.681 --> 35:30.181
in the bathroom anyway.

35:31.684 --> 35:35.920
And these...
Desna, these are incredible.

35:35.955 --> 35:39.323
They are exactly
what I'm thinking and feeling.

35:39.358 --> 35:41.892
This is why I want to open my new place.

35:41.928 --> 35:44.895
I want more women to experience that.

35:44.931 --> 35:47.064
Then I want to franchise!

35:47.100 --> 35:48.499
What?!

35:48.534 --> 35:49.600
Girl!

35:49.635 --> 35:51.402
Yes!

35:53.139 --> 35:55.139
Okay, I will talk to Mrs. Kim

35:55.174 --> 35:57.942
and see if I can make anything happen.

35:57.977 --> 36:00.311
- Thank you.
- Okay.

36:00.346 --> 36:02.746
Now I'm gonna go try a little dancing.

36:02.782 --> 36:04.448
Go get it!

36:04.484 --> 36:07.852
Go, Mandy! Go, Mandy!

36:10.823 --> 36:13.491
These bourgie types can throw down.

36:15.294 --> 36:19.730
The last time I danced with
Roller was up on that stage.

36:22.168 --> 36:23.767
I know, baby.

36:28.708 --> 36:30.040
Hello?

36:30.076 --> 36:32.309
Get your ass to the clinic.

36:32.345 --> 36:34.879
Bring Goldilocks, too.

36:34.914 --> 36:37.314
Shit. We got to go. Now.

36:43.531 --> 36:47.855
I struggle to grasp...

36:48.794 --> 36:50.172
how something like this could happen.

36:50.196 --> 36:52.229
This guy was having a seizure.

36:52.265 --> 36:54.798
The delivery guy seemed so legit.

36:54.834 --> 36:55.834
Desna, where were you?

36:58.804 --> 37:01.572
I had a full house at the salon, Clay.

37:01.607 --> 37:03.538
Full house?

37:05.578 --> 37:08.012
Why don't you tell them
what you found there, Juanda?

37:08.047 --> 37:11.515
We're looking at an $88,000 loss.

37:11.551 --> 37:14.318
- Man.
- But this is particularly staggering af...

37:14.924 --> 37:16.687
after what happened.

37:16.722 --> 37:19.223
Baby. Go ahead and say it, baby.

37:19.258 --> 37:21.425
What happened to our baby boy...

37:22.595 --> 37:24.392
What happened to our Roller.

37:25.298 --> 37:26.497
Got murdered.

37:30.403 --> 37:35.039
Meanwhile... that little tiny
dancer of his

37:35.862 --> 37:38.781
looks like she got shit out a python.

37:42.682 --> 37:46.998
Y'all know hhhow expensive
this all gonna be?

37:48.888 --> 37:51.021
This here... This here clinic...

37:51.057 --> 37:54.058
It was supposed to be the best thing

37:54.093 --> 37:56.460
that ever happened to this family.

38:03.236 --> 38:04.768
Y'all gonna have to work this off.

38:04.804 --> 38:06.971
W... That's not fair!
Well, life's not fair.

38:07.006 --> 38:08.739
Mr. Husser, I wasn't even there.

38:08.774 --> 38:10.741
You were on duty, Kenneth.

38:10.776 --> 38:12.020
And Desna here... You're supposed to be

38:12.044 --> 38:13.444
giving my boy the lay of the land.

38:13.479 --> 38:15.946
And Bryce... Bryce.

38:15.982 --> 38:17.948
My boy Bryce...

38:17.984 --> 38:19.283
You're supposed to be

38:19.318 --> 38:22.200
running this goddamn clinic!

38:23.475 --> 38:25.330
This is disgraceful!

38:25.992 --> 38:27.992
God damn it!

38:29.061 --> 38:32.896
Disgraceful, all y'all.

38:36.102 --> 38:37.768
I will have what I am owed.

38:55.649 --> 38:57.382
Hey, what are you looking for?

39:00.020 --> 39:02.721
Look, I'm stuck, all right?

39:02.756 --> 39:04.089
$80,000 is stuck.

39:04.124 --> 39:05.824
Only as stuck as you want to be,

39:05.859 --> 39:08.412
Mr. Power of Intentional Choice.

39:09.430 --> 39:11.174
I never should have asked Desna
to train you.

39:11.198 --> 39:13.799
I messed up again with Uncle Daddy

39:13.834 --> 39:16.334
when he was trying to help me again.

39:16.370 --> 39:18.236
He knew this was temporary,
he didn't like it,

39:18.272 --> 39:20.150
- now you're indentured for life.
- Come on, honey.

39:20.174 --> 39:22.107
TThat's a little reachyreachy,
isn't it?

39:22.142 --> 39:23.942
I wouldn't put it past him.

39:23.977 --> 39:25.877
What are you looking for?

39:28.315 --> 39:29.600
What is that?

39:30.884 --> 39:32.384
Honey!

39:32.419 --> 39:33.852
Sweetie?

39:33.887 --> 39:36.521
Babe. No, no, no.

39:36.557 --> 39:37.789
Don't you do it. H...

39:37.825 --> 39:40.444
Babe, it's been two years.

39:40.994 --> 39:43.962
Well, this is what this nonsense
is doing to me.

40:25.072 --> 40:28.140
Back to the corner, allemande left.

40:33.380 --> 40:36.047
For the ladies, starting on the left.

40:38.051 --> 40:41.086
When you meet your partner,
turn to my right.

40:42.723 --> 40:43.989
Back to the corner...

40:48.896 --> 40:50.228
Hey, party animal.

40:50.264 --> 40:52.030
Thank you for an incredible night.

40:53.767 --> 40:55.834
Honey, we lived.

40:55.869 --> 40:59.104
Girl, I haven't lived
like that since the '90s.

40:59.139 --> 41:01.773
So, what's up?

41:01.808 --> 41:05.143
Desna, I'm in. You got me.

41:05.179 --> 41:07.879
I'm gonna find you
the best salon in town.

41:07.915 --> 41:10.282
Yeah, screw Glint Nails.

41:11.535 --> 41:14.452
I believe in you and your vision.

41:14.488 --> 41:16.087
All right, thanks, Mandy.

41:16.123 --> 41:17.956
You got it. I'll talk to you later.

41:22.029 --> 41:24.930
What? What?

41:24.965 --> 41:26.298
I got Mandy back!

41:26.333 --> 41:29.568
Yes, girl! I knew you would!

41:29.603 --> 41:30.635
Where's Jenn?

41:30.660 --> 41:32.404
I don't know. Her
car's outside, though.

41:32.439 --> 41:34.272
Well, she better get her butt in here...

41:34.308 --> 41:36.041
'Cause we doing big things.

41:36.076 --> 41:37.042
That's right!

41:37.077 --> 41:39.144
New salon, new life.

41:39.179 --> 41:42.180
Dosido your partner.

41:42.216 --> 41:45.116
Back to your corner, allemande left.

41:45.152 --> 41:47.252
And right, left grand.

41:49.656 --> 41:52.824
When you reach your partner,
swing her and promenade.

42:06.440 --> 42:08.840
Hey! Come join the fun, neighbor.

42:08.875 --> 42:11.743
Yeah, not really a black thing.

42:15.716 --> 42:17.682
I'm sorry, Des.

42:17.718 --> 42:19.584
I'm just trying to distract myself

42:19.620 --> 42:21.119
from becoming a widow.

42:21.154 --> 42:22.554
Mnhmnh. Don't say that.

42:22.589 --> 42:24.756
Bryce has a good head on his shoulders.

42:24.791 --> 42:28.526
Baby, Bryce is a drug addict
just recovered.

42:28.562 --> 42:30.762
He doesn't have so much
as a criminal pinky bone

42:30.797 --> 42:32.097
in his whole body.

42:32.132 --> 42:33.465
If the Dixie Mafia don't get him,

42:33.500 --> 42:34.966
then all those pills will,

42:35.002 --> 42:38.069
and it's gonna take us so long
to pay back Uncle Daddy.

42:38.105 --> 42:40.305
I'm sorry. I'm sorry I wasn't there

42:40.340 --> 42:41.740
to keep an eye on him.

42:41.775 --> 42:44.075
It's not your fault, babe.
You can't be everywhere.

42:44.111 --> 42:47.012
I know you want out from under
this mess just as much as I do.

42:47.047 --> 42:51.683
God, I want that. I want it so bad.

42:51.718 --> 42:54.853
I want to get the salon.
I want to live the dream.

42:54.888 --> 42:56.888
I...

42:56.923 --> 42:58.657
I want it for all of us.

42:58.692 --> 43:02.160
Do you think we're gonna be
stuck in Husserville forever?

43:02.771 --> 43:04.296
I know we won't.

43:04.331 --> 43:07.866
That family is like quicksand.

43:07.901 --> 43:11.202
The more you struggle,
the more they just suck you in.

43:11.238 --> 43:13.738
Come here. Don't cry.

43:38.265 --> 43:39.864
They're here.

43:49.176 --> 43:50.809
Set it down.

44:00.135 --> 44:02.620
Worked like a charm, didn't it?

44:02.656 --> 44:04.356
Yes, sir.

44:05.158 --> 44:07.625
I knew it would.

44:08.212 --> 44:09.494
That's for you.

44:12.299 --> 44:13.264
Thank you, sir.

44:13.300 --> 44:15.700
Get you going.

45:20.467 --> 45:22.801
What took you so long?

45:27.274 --> 45:29.607
I missed you, baby girl.

45:36.783 --> 45:40.051
I missed you, too, baby.
I missed you so much.

